Canyon Capital Advisors, LLC Key Developments

Canyon Capital Advisors, LLC Presents at 2016 Wells Fargo Middle Market Opportunities Forum, Dec-08-2016 11:15 AM
Sep 16 16
Canyon Capital Advisors, LLC Presents at 2016 Wells Fargo Middle Market Opportunities Forum, Dec-08-2016 11:15 AM. Venue: The Plaza Hotel, New York, New York, United States. Speakers: Joshua Stephan Friedman, Founding Partner, Co-Chairman, and Co-Chief Executive Officer.


Canyon Capital Advisors Seeking Sale of Assets In Yahoo!
Jan 15 16
Canyon Capital Advisors, LLC, an investor in Yahoo! Inc. (NasdaqGS:YHOO) is seeking a sale of Yahoo's core business, assets or the whole company, according to the letter obtained by Reuters. "We believe the board must explicitly and publicly commit to preserve the company's most easily valued asset - its cash," Canyon Capital wrote in the letter. According to sources earlier this month, Starboard Value posted a similar letter earlier this month.


Strada And Angel To Reportedly Sell Two Downtown Oakland Office Buildings
Oct 8 15
Strada Investment Group, LLC and Angelo, Gordon & Co. are in contract to sell two downtown Oakland office buildings for around $115 million to Rubicon Point Partners, LLC and its financial partner Canyon Capital Advisors, LLC, according to sources familiar with the properties. Strada declined to comment.


